query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('activemq',
'aes',
'constraints',
'css',
'focus',
'glassfish',
'google-cloud-datastore',
'html5',
'json',
'login',
'sitecore',
'templates',
'vb6',
'wolfram-mathematica',
'xsd');
